current-chamber.#text: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

official-title.#text:
To prohibit the sale, lease, transfer, retransfer, or
		  delivery of F–16 aircraft, M1 tanks, or certain other defense articles or
		  services to the Government of Egypt.

sponsor.#tail:
introduced the
			 following bill; which was read the first time

action-desc.#text:
Read the second time and placed on the
			 calendar

Read the second time and placed on the
		  calendar

header.#text:
Prohibition on certain
			 military sales to Egypt

text.#text:
Notwithstanding any
			 other provision of law, the United States Government shall not license,
			 approve, facilitate, or otherwise allow the sale, lease, transfer, retransfer,
			 or delivery of F–16 aircraft, M1 tanks, or other defense articles or services
			 listed in Category VI, VII, or VIII of the United States Munitions List to the
			 Government of Egypt.

term.#tail: means the list referred to in

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#text:
section 38(a)(1) of
			 the Arms Export Control Act
